s\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Saud Razzak\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17977:\"<p>Do you want to know how to verify your WordPress website with Pinterest?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Pinterest is the world&#8217;s third-largest search engine after Google and YouTube. By verifying your website on Pinterest, you can drive more organic traffic from Pinterest to your site.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this tutorial, we’ll show you how to easily verify your website on Pinterest.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So let’s dig in.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Why Should You Verify Your Website on Pinterest?</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Verify-your-WordPress-website-with-Pinterest.jpg\" alt=\"Verify your WordPress website with Pinterest\" class=\"wp-image-45896\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Verify-your-WordPress-website-with-Pinterest.jpg 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Verify-your-WordPress-website-with-Pinterest-300x171.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Verify-your-WordPress-website-with-Pinterest-600x343.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Verify-your-WordPress-website-with-Pinterest-105x60.jpg 105w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Verify-your-WordPress-website-with-Pinterest-158x90.jpg 158w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Pinterest is mostly used by people who are searching for visual content to discover new ideas, inspiration or learn something new.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As many as <strong>450 million</strong> users prefer the platform to share images, GIFs, videos, and related types of visual content.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If your website focuses on visual arts such as photography or an eCommerce store, Pinterest can significantly increase your web traffic and brand visibility.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>How to Easily Verify Your WordPress Site With Pinterest</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We have created this simple tutorial that covers all steps of the process. If you want to jump straight to a specific step, you can use these quick links:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"#Upgrade-Your-Pinterest-Account-to-Business\">Step 1. Upgrade Your Pinterest Account to Business</a></li><li><a href=\"#Claim-Your-Website-on-Pinterest\">Step 2. Claim Your Website on Pinterest</a></li><li><a href=\"#Add-HTML-Tag-to-Your-WordPress-Website\">Step 3. Add HTML Tag to Your WordPress Website</a></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"Upgrade-Your-Pinterest-Account-to-Business\">Step 1. Upgrade Your Pinterest Account to Business</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>First things first, you should upgrade your personal account to a Pinterest business account.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A <a href=\"https://business.pinterest.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Pinterest business account</a> lets you gain access to a lot of Pinterest benefits that you wouldn’t have otherwise, including boosting brand authority, driving traffic, the ability to create and display ads, access to Pinterest insights, and more.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Best of all, <strong>Pinterest Business</strong> is free and easy to set up.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>By default, all Pinterest account is a personal account. To claim your website on Pinterest, you&#8217;ll have to switch your personal account to a business account. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Switch From Personal to Business</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Log in to your Pinterest account, go to the top right corner, and click the dropdown arrow.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here you need to click the <strong>Convert to Business</strong> link.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"620\" height=\"285\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Convert-to-Business.png\" alt=\"Convert to business\" class=\"wp-image-45898\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Convert-to-Business.png 620w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Convert-to-Business-300x138.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Convert-to-Business-600x276.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Convert-to-Business-131x60.png 131w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Convert-to-Business-196x90.png 196w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>On the next screen, you can see all the personal and business account features, with the business account offering more features.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"306\" height=\"285\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Click-Convert-Account-Button.png\" alt=\"Click to the Convert account\" class=\"wp-image-45899\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Click-Convert-Account-Button.png 306w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Click-Convert-Account-Button-300x279.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Click-Convert-Account-Button-64x60.png 64w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Click-Convert-Account-Button-97x90.png 97w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 306px) 100vw, 306px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Next, click the <strong>Convert Account</strong> button. It will take you to a new screen where you need to create a business profile.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>After that, add your business details such as business name, website, country, and language.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"447\" height=\"391\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Build-your-profile.png\" alt=\"Build your profile\" class=\"wp-image-45900\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Build-your-profile.png 447w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Build-your-profile-300x262.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Build-your-profile-69x60.png 69w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Build-your-profile-103x90.png 103w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 447px) 100vw, 447px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Next, you need to describe your business and the goals you wish to achieve with the Pinterest business account. These goals could be driving traffic to your site, generating more leads for your business, or more sales.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"349\" height=\"276\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Describe-your-Goals-1.png\" alt=\"Describe your goal\" class=\"wp-image-45901\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Describe-your-Goals-1.png 349w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Describe-your-Goals-1-300x237.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Describe-your-Goals-1-76x60.png 76w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Describe-your-Goals-1-114x90.png 114w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 349px) 100vw, 349px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>On the next screen, you need to describe who you’re (choose from blogger, store owner, influencer), and click <strong>Next</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"347\" height=\"341\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Describe-your-business.png\" alt=\"Describe your business\" class=\"wp-image-45902\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Describe-your-business.png 347w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Describe-your-business-300x295.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Describe-your-business-61x60.png 61w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Describe-your-business-92x90.png 92w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 347px) 100vw, 347px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Now select <strong>Yes</strong>, if you wish to run ads on Pinterest. In our case, we’re selecting <strong>No </strong>because we don’t want to advertise at the moment. Click <strong>Next</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"547\" height=\"352\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Running-ads-on-Pinterest.png\" alt=\"Running ads on Pinterest\" class=\"wp-image-45903\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Running-ads-on-Pinterest.png 547w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Running-ads-on-Pinterest-300x193.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Running-ads-on-Pinterest-93x60.png 93w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Running-ads-on-Pinterest-140x90.png 140w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 547px) 100vw, 547px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Now Pinterest will ask you where you would like to start. Here we can see <strong>3</strong> options, including sharing ideas, claiming your website, and showcasing your brand.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For this tutorial, we’re selecting <strong>Claim your Website</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"620\" height=\"470\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Choose-Claim-your-website.png\" alt=\"Claim your website\" class=\"wp-image-45904\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Choose-Claim-your-website.png 620w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Choose-Claim-your-website-300x227.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Choose-Claim-your-website-600x455.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Choose-Claim-your-website-79x60.png 79w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Choose-Claim-your-website-119x90.png 119w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Now let’s move to the next step and see how you can easily claim your WordPress website on Pinterest.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"Claim-Your-Website-on-Pinterest\">Step 2. Claim Your Website on Pinterest</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>On this screen, you can see the <strong>Claim</strong> button next to the website. It will directly take you to the claim settings page.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"620\" height=\"328\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Select-Websites-Claims.png\" alt=\"Select website claim\" class=\"wp-image-45905\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Select-Websites-Claims.png 620w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Select-Websites-Claims-300x159.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Select-Websites-Claims-600x317.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Select-Websites-Claims-113x60.png 113w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Select-Websites-Claims-170x90.png 170w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>After clicking the <strong>Claim</strong> button, Pinterest will show you a popup with the options for finalizing the claim process.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can see <strong>3</strong> methods including:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Add HTML tag — </strong>simply add an HTML code snippet to your website &lt;head&gt; section.</li><li><strong>Upload HTML file — </strong>download an HTML file and upload it to the root directory of your website.</li><li><strong>Add TXT record —</strong> add a verification record to your domain host.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"696\" height=\"388\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Choose-how-you-want-to-claim.png\" alt=\"Choose how you want to claim\" class=\"wp-image-45906\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Choose-how-you-want-to-claim.png 696w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Choose-how-you-want-to-claim-300x167.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Choose-how-you-want-to-claim-600x334.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Choose-how-you-want-to-claim-108x60.png 108w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Choose-how-you-want-to-claim-161x90.png 161w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 696px) 100vw, 696px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>While you can opt for any of the three methods, we will use the first <strong>HTML tag</strong> addition method since it is the simplest of the three options.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"Add-HTML-Tag-to-Your-WordPress-Website\">Step 3. Add HTML Tag to Your WordPress Website</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>To add the HTML tag, you can install the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\">AIl In One SEO plugin</a> on your WordPress website. For more details, see the detailed guide on <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/beginners-guide/step-by-step-guide-to-install-a-wordpress-plugin-for-beginners/\">how to install a WordPress plugin</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"730\" height=\"447\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-2.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO plugin\" class=\"wp-image-45907\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-2.png 730w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-2-300x184.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-2-600x367.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-2-98x60.png 98w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-2-147x90.png 147w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 730px) 100vw, 730px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you’ve done with plugin installation, navigate to <strong>WordPress Dashboard » General Setting » Webmaster Tools</strong> and select the <strong>Pinterest Site Verification</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"620\" height=\"245\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-WebMaster-Tool.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO webmaster tools\" class=\"wp-image-45908\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-WebMaster-Tool.png 620w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-WebMaster-Tool-300x119.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-WebMaster-Tool-600x237.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-WebMaster-Tool-152x60.png 152w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-WebMaster-Tool-228x90.png 228w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Once selected, the verification tab will appear on the same screen. Here you need to copy the code from Pinterest and paste it into the <strong>Pinterest Verification Code. </strong>Click <strong>Save Changes</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"620\" height=\"269\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Pinterest-Verification-code.png\" alt=\"Pinterest verification code\" class=\"wp-image-45909\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Pinterest-Verification-code.png 620w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Pinterest-Verification-code-300x130.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Pinterest-Verification-code-600x260.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Pinterest-Verification-code-138x60.png 138w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Pinterest-Verification-code-207x90.png 207w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Go back to Pinterest and click <strong>Continue</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"620\" height=\"345\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/click-continue-button.png\" alt=\"Click to the continue button\" class=\"wp-image-45910\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/click-continue-button.png 620w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/click-continue-button-300x167.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/click-continue-button-600x334.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/click-continue-button-108x60.png 108w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/click-continue-button-162x90.png 162w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Next, Pinterest asks you to verify your website by adding your site link. Once added, click <strong>Verify</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"620\" height=\"341\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Click-Verify-Button.png\" alt=\"Click to the Verify button\" class=\"wp-image-45911\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Click-Verify-Button.png 620w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Click-Verify-Button-300x165.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Click-Verify-Button-600x330.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Click-Verify-Button-109x60.png 109w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Click-Verify-Button-164x90.png 164w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It will take a few seconds to finalize the process. Once verified, you will see the verification message.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"659\" height=\"324\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Verification-in-Progress.png\" alt=\"Verification in Progress\" class=\"wp-image-45912\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Verification-in-Progress.png 659w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Verification-in-Progress-300x147.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Verification-in-Progress-600x295.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Verification-in-Progress-122x60.png 122w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Verification-in-Progress-183x90.png 183w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 659px) 100vw, 659px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Congratulations!</strong> Your website has now been claimed successfully.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this article helped you verify your WordPress website with Pinterest. Use this tutorial, and it’ll help drive more referral traffic to your website, boost engagement, and build your brand at rocket speed.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You may also want to check out our post on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-integrate-social-media-into-your-website/\">how to integrate social media into your website</a> and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-best-optimize-images-in-wordpress/\">how to best optimize your images in WordPress</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Not using <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\">AIOSEO</a> yet? What are you waiting for?</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-verify-your-wordpress-website-with-pinterest/\">How to Verify Your WordPress Website With Pinterest (Step by Step)</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-verify-your-wordpress-website-with-pinterest/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:44:\"7 Best WordPress Redirect Plugins (Compared)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s: