-plugins/\">7 Best WordPress Redirect Plugins (Compared)</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Saud Razzak\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19177:\"<p>Looking to find the best WordPress redirect plugins for your site?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>There are various reasons when you need to create a redirect.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>You want to redirect users to another page because the original page no longer exists. </li><li>You want to revamp a page and temporarily move your visitors to a different page.</li><li>You’ve changed the post or page URL and want the visitors to see the new URL.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>In simple words, you just need to make sure the visitors don’t leave your site without getting the information they are looking for.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this post, we’ll show you some of the best redirection plugins and help you choose the right plugin for your WordPress website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are some quick links to what we’ll cover in this article. If you’re in a hurry, you can jump directly to the section you want to read.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"#What-Is-a-Redirection-in-WordPress\">What Is a Redirection in WordPress?</a></li><li><a href=\"#Best-WordPress-Redirect-Plugins\">Best WordPress Redirect Plugins (2021)</a></li><li><a href=\"#Best-Redirect-Plugin-for-Your-WordPress-Site\">Best Redirect Plugin for Your WordPress Site</a></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Let’s dig in.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"What-Is-a-Redirection-in-WordPress\">What Is a Redirect in WordPress?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A redirect in WordPress is the best way to tell web browsers that the requested page can be found at a different location.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As a result, the browser automatically loads the page from the new location without impacting the user experience.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>There are several types of redirects, with the following three being the most common on WordPress websites:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>301 Redirect:</strong> Indicates that the resource has been permanently moved to a new location.</li><li><strong>302 Redirect:</strong> Indicates that the resource has temporarily moved to a new location but the HTTP method can be changed.</li><li><strong>307 Redirect:</strong> Indicates that the resource has temporarily moved to a new location but the HTTP method should remain the same.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>By using WordPress redirect, you can rest assured that your users won&#8217;t see <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-easily-find-and-fix-404-errors-in-wordpress/\">404 Page Not Found Error</a> and doesn&#8217;t affect search rankings. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Alright! Now you know why you need to use a redirect. Let’s get into the list.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"Best-WordPress-Redirect-Plugins\">Best WordPress Redirect Plugins (2021)</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are the top 7 WordPress redirect plugins that we’re going to check out so that you can pick the best fit for your site.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>1. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\">All in One SEO for WordPress (AIOSEO)</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"730\" height=\"447\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-2.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO - Best WordPress Redirect Plugins\" class=\"wp-image-45907\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-2.png 730w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-2-300x184.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-2-600x367.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-2-98x60.png 98w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-2-147x90.png 147w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 730px) 100vw, 730px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\"></a></p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\">AIOSEO</a> is a popular WordPress SEO plugin that allows you to set up redirections with a single click.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The plugin comes with a simple redirect manager to easily manage all types of redirections without writing a single line of code.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>All you need to do is go to the <strong>WordPress Dashboard » All In One SEO » Redirects</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"620\" height=\"261\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-Redirect-Settings.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO Redirects Settings\" class=\"wp-image-45923\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-Redirect-Settings.png 620w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-Redirect-Settings-300x126.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-Redirect-Settings-600x253.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-Redirect-Settings-143x60.png 143w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-Redirect-Settings-214x90.png 214w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can add any type of redirection by simply adding the URLs and selecting the type of redirection.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Easy peasy!!</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features</strong><strong>:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Import and Export Redirection:</strong> Import and export redirection from other plugins. For more details, check out our guide on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/import-and-export-redirects-in-wordpress/\">how to easily import and export redirects in WordPress</a>.</li><li><strong>Check Redirect:</strong> AIOSEO’s redirection manager comes with a built-in redirect checker. This allows you to quickly check if your redirects are working properly.</li><li><strong>Automatic Redirects:</strong> You can set the automatic redirects to your posts and pages.</li><li><strong>Logs:</strong> You can check the records of all redirects to see all the useful information.</li><li><strong>Full Site Redirect:</strong> You can easily redirect your entire site in a few clicks. Everything will be redirected except WordPress login and admin.</li><li><strong>Local SEO:</strong> It tells Google about your business, including business name, email address, location, hours, and price range.</li><li><strong>Breadcrumbs Navigation:</strong> This allows you to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/displaying-breadcrumbs-on-your-site/\">display breadcrumbs</a> exactly the way you want and thus improves the user experience on your website.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>This is not all &#8211; AIOSEO comes with all the essential features to optimize your website for search engines. You can check out the complete <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/\">features of AIOSEO</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong><strong>:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>AIOSEO offers <strong>4</strong> different plans. The starting price of this plugin is <strong>$49.50 </strong>per year.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>2. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/yoast-premium/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Yoast SEO</a></h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/yoast-premium/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"611\" height=\"301\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Yoast-SEO-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-45924\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Yoast-SEO-1.png 611w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Yoast-SEO-1-300x148.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Yoast-SEO-1-600x296.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Yoast-SEO-1-122x60.png 122w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Yoast-SEO-1-183x90.png 183w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 611px) 100vw, 611px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://yoast.com/wordpress/plugins/seo/\"></a></p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/yoast-premium/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Yoast</a> is yet another SEO plugin that also lets you easily set up WordPress redirection on your website. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Just as AIOSEO, Yoast also allows you to choose from several different types of redirections with a few clicks. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features</strong><strong>:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Automatic Redirects:</strong> This plugin offers automatic redirects when you move the post and pages of your WordPress websites.</li><li><strong>Manage Redirects:</strong> You can manage your redirects in your site admin, where you can search and filter the list.</li><li><strong>Import and Export Redirect:</strong> You can easily import and export redirects in CSV format.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Aside from redirection management, Yoast also comes bundled with essential SEO features, such as optimize articles for keywords and keyphrases, the ability to write meta tags, structured data blocks, and more. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong><strong>:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>The pricing for a <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/yoast-premium/\">single site license</a> starts at <strong>$89</strong> per year.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>3. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/redirection/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Redirection</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/redirection/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"691\" height=\"310\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Redirection-Plugin-WordPress.png\" alt=\"Redirection Plugin WordPress\" class=\"wp-image-46569\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Redirection-Plugin-WordPress.png 691w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Redirection-Plugin-WordPress-300x135.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Redirection-Plugin-WordPress-600x269.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Redirection-Plugin-WordPress-134x60.png 134w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Redirection-Plugin-WordPress-201x90.png 201w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 691px) 100vw, 691px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/redirection/\"></a></p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/redirection/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Redirection</a> is a free WordPress plugin that allows you to manage redirects on your WordPress website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition, it allows conditional redirects with dozens of possibilities like server redirect, role capability redirect, page type redirects, IP address redirect, login status redirect, and more.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You don’t need to be a WordPress expert to use this plugin, as it is easy to set up.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features</strong><strong>:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Import and Export:</strong> This plugin supports the import and export of the redirection.</li><li><strong>Migrate Permalinks:</strong> It allows you to migrate old permalinks simply by entering the old permalinks structure.</li><li><strong>Limited Migration: </strong>This plugin offers limited redirect migration from other SEO plugins.</li><li><strong>Complicated UI: </strong>New users might find it challenging to navigate with the UI.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong><strong>:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>The plugin is available for free.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>4. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/rank-math/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Rank Math</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/rank-math/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"301\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/RankMath-1.png\" alt=\"RankMath\" class=\"wp-image-45926\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/RankMath-1.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/RankMath-1-300x129.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/RankMath-1-600x258.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/RankMath-1-140x60.png 140w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/RankMath-1-209x90.png 209w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://rankmath.com/\"></a></p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/rank-math/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Rank Math</a> is another WordPress SEO plugin that offers the redirect feature. This plugin is very similar to Yoast. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The major drawback of this plugin is it only supports <strong>3</strong> redirect types. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features</strong><strong>:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>404 Error: </strong>It allows you to monitor your site for 404 errors.</li><li><strong>Custom Redirection:</strong> You can set up custom redirects for any page you need.</li><li><strong>Simple and Clean:</strong> Easy setup wizard and simple and clean UI.</li><li><strong>Manage Redirects:</strong> It allows you to easily create, manage, enable, or disable redirects at any scale.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Pricing for a single site license starts at <strong>$59</strong> per year.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>5. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/https-redirection/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Easy HTTPS Redirection (SSL)</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/https-redirection/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"658\" height=\"294\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Easy-HTTPS-Redirection