ly URL Structure in WordPress</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What are you waiting for? Get started with the most powerful <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\">WordPress AIOSEO plugin</a> today.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-wordpress-redirect-plugins/\">7 Best WordPress Redirect Plugins (Compared)</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"https://aioseo.com/best-wordpress-redirect-plugins/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"How to Create WordPress Image Sitemap (In a Single Click)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:138:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-create-wordpress-image-sitemap/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=how-to-create-wordpress-image-sitemap\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-create-wordpress-image-sitemap/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 08 Jul 2021 14:25:15 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:3:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"All in One SEO Pack\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"Create a WordPress Image Sitemap\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:23:\"Image Sitemap WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"https://aioseo.com/?p=45688\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:431:\"<p>Are you wondering what is an image sitemap and how you can create one on your WordPress website? Image sitemap is an ideal solution for websites that have multiple images on several pages. The best part is that it helps&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-create-wordpress-image-sitemap/\">How to Create WordPress Image Sitemap (In a Single Click)</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Saud Razzak\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8830:\"<p>Are you wondering what is an image sitemap and how you can create one on your WordPress website?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Image sitemap is an ideal solution for websites that have multiple images on several pages. The best part is that it helps search engines discover your images that they might not find otherwise.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this post, we’ll explain what a WordPress image sitemap is and why you need to create one for your website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here’s a quick overview of what we’ll cover in this article. Feel free to jump directly to the section that you want to read.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"#What-Is-an-Image-Sitemap\">What Is an Image Sitemap?</a></li><li><a href=\"#Why-You-Should-Create-WordPress-Image-Sitemap\">Why You Should Create WordPress Image Sitemap</a></li><li><a href=\"#How-to-Create-a-Sitemap-in-WordPress\">How to Create a Sitemap in WordPress</a></li><li><a href=\"#Use-the-Best-Image-Sitemap-Generator-Plugin-AIOSEO\">Use the Best Image Sitemap Generator Plugin AIOSEO</a></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"What-Is-an-Image-Sitemap\">What Is an Image Sitemap?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>An image sitemap is a file that contains all information about the images present on your website in a format that Google can easily go through. Usually, this sitemap includes essential information such as image format, caption, and title.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With a sitemap, you create a structured record of the images available on your website. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>As you can imagine, the image sitemap makes your website more crawlable, and help your images appear in Google search results. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"Why-You-Should-Create-WordPress-Image-Sitemap\">Why You Should Create WordPress Image Sitemap</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Every website owner wants to see their pages as high in the Google search results as possible. Images make your site more visible on Google in placeslike <strong>Google Image Search</strong> and <strong>Image Snippets</strong> section appearing in Google search ranking pages.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here&#8217;re a few other reasons why you need to create a WordPress image sitemap:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Your site is large, so you&#8217;re afraid Google might overlook the images you&#8217;ve added in your recent pages</li><li>You want to make your site SEO-friendly and ensure Google can easily crawl your images more efficiently</li><li>You want to have more control over the information that Google displays about your website’s images.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"How-to-Create-a-Sitemap-in-WordPress\">How to Create a Sitemap in WordPress</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"730\" height=\"345\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-1.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO\" class=\"wp-image-45889\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-1.png 730w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-1-300x142.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-1-600x284.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-1-127x60.png 127w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-1-190x90.png 190w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 730px) 100vw, 730px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Using the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\">All In One SEO (AIOSEO)</a> plugin is the easiest way to create an image sitemap on your WordPress website.  </p>\n\n\n\n<p>AIOSEO also allows you to create <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-create-a-video-sitemap-in-wordpress-the-easy-way/\">video sitemaps</a>, <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/submit-your-site-to-google-news/\">Google News sitemaps</a>, and comes with tons of different SEO tools. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>With that said, let’s see how you can create WordPress image sitemaps on your website.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Creating Your Image Sitemap With AIOSEO Plugin</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>First things first, you need to install and activate the AIOSEO plugin on your WordPress website. For more details, see the WPBeginner <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/beginners-guide/step-by-step-guide-to-install-a-wordpress-plugin-for-beginners/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">guide on properly installing and setting up a WordPress plugin</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you have installed the AIOSEO plugin on your website, the next step is to go to <strong>WordPress Dashboard » Navigate » Sitemaps.</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>On this screen, you can see different sitemap options; however, in this article, we’ll focus on the image sitemaps.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"620\" height=\"312\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-sitemaps.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO Sitemaps Setting\" class=\"wp-image-45890\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-sitemaps.png 620w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-sitemaps-300x151.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-sitemaps-600x302.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-sitemaps-119x60.png 119w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/AIOSEO-sitemaps-179x90.png 179w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Scroll down to the <strong>General Sitemaps</strong> setting page and go to the <strong>Advanced Settings </strong>tab. Toggle on to see the image sitemap setting.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"620\" height=\"138\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/advance-settings.png\" alt=\"Advanced settings\" class=\"wp-image-45891\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/advance-settings.png 620w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/advance-settings-300x67.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/advance-settings-600x134.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/advance-settings-190x42.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/advance-settings-404x90.png 404w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you’re done with that, you need to make sure that the <strong>Exclude Images</strong> button is set to <strong>No</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> By default, AIOSEO sitemap includes all the website images within the <strong>XML Sitemap</strong> that is submitted to the search engine.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"620\" height=\"256\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/xml-sitemap-images.png\" alt=\"XML Sitemaps Images\" class=\"wp-image-45892\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/xml-sitemap-images.png 620w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/xml-sitemap-images-300x124.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/xml-sitemap-images-600x248.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/xml-sitemap-images-145x60.png 145w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/xml-sitemap-images-218x90.png 218w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>If the image sitemap is already set to <strong>No</strong>, click the toggle to set it <strong>Yes </strong>if you want to exclude the images from the sitemap. Our recommendation is to keep the images indexable within the sitemap.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Once done, click the <strong>Save Changes</strong> button.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"620\" height=\"110\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/exclude-image.png\" alt=\"Exclude Image\" class=\"wp-image-45893\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/exclude-image.png 620w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/exclude-image-300x53.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/exclude-image-600x106.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/exclude-image-190x34.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/exclude-image-507x90.png 507w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"Use-the-Best-Image-Sitemap-Generator-Plugin-AIOSEO\">Use the Best Image Sitemap Generator Plugin AIOSEO</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Adding images to the sitemap is a good strategy to increase your brand&#8217;s exposure on Google and other search engines.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this post helped you understand how to create an image sitemap on your WordPress website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can go ahead and check out the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/\">All In One SEO&#8217;s</a> sitemap feature and share your experience with us.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And if you want to learn more about SEO, please also visit our<a href=\"https://aioseo.com/ultimate-wordpress-seo-guide/\"> ultimate WordPress SEO guide.</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>What are you waiting for? Get started with the most powerful <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\">WordPress AIOSEO plugin</a> today.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-create-wordpress-image-sitemap/\">How to Create WordPress Image Sitemap (In a Single Click)</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-create-wordpress-image-sitemap/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"7 Best WooCommerce SEO Plugins And Tools to Get More Traffic\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"