It improves user experience by telling your visitors on which page they&#8217;re relative to the homepage.&#160; In terms of SEO,&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-breadcrumbs-plugins-for-wordpress/\">7 Best Breadcrumbs Plugins for WordPress (in 2021)</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Saud Razzak\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21815:\"<p>Are you looking for the best breadcrumbs plugin for your WordPress website?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Using breadcrumbs on your site has 2 benefits:&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>It improves user experience by telling your visitors on which page they&#8217;re relative to the homepage.&nbsp;</li><li>In terms of SEO, it enables you to show a breadcrumb trail in the search results, which makes your site stand out.&nbsp;</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>In this post, we’ll share some of the best WordPress breadcrumbs plugins that will help improve user experience throughout your website.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>What Are Breadcrumbs in WordPress?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Breadcrumbs on a WordPress website present a simple path that the visitors could follow from their current location to the previous pages, all the way to the home page.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As a result, visitors can easily go back to any of the pages that lie in the path to the top-level pages.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here’s an example of breadcrumbs:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"950\" height=\"446\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/example-of-breadcrumbs.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-43906\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/example-of-breadcrumbs.png 950w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/example-of-breadcrumbs-300x141.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/example-of-breadcrumbs-768x361.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/example-of-breadcrumbs-600x282.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/example-of-breadcrumbs-128x60.png 128w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/example-of-breadcrumbs-192x90.png 192w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can see that the breadcrumbs (highlighted in the box) <strong>WPBeginner » Blog » Tutorials</strong> allow the reader to go to either tutorials, blog, or the top-level homepage by clicking any of the links.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Using these links, visitors can easily go to any page in the chain without wasting time searching for it or clicking the <strong>Back</strong> button.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Breadcrumbs are a secondary navigation feature that supports the main website navigation and presents a simple scheme that visitors could follow to the previous pages.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>While you can implement breadcrumbs manually, the best practice is to use a plugin that sets up the feature for your website.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are <strong>7</strong> WordPress breadcrumbs plugins to help you implement the feature without any hassle.</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><a href=\"#All-In-One-SEO\">All In One SEO</a></li><li><a href=\"#Yoast-SEO\">Yoast SEO</a>&nbsp;</li><li><a href=\"#RankMath\">RankMath</a></li><li><a href=\"#Breadcrumb-NavXT\">Breadcrumb NavXT</a></li><li><a href=\"#Breadcrumb\">Breadcrumb</a></li><li><a href=\"#Flexy-Breadcrumb\">Flexy Breadcrumb</a></li><li><a href=\"#WooCommerce-Breadcrumbs\">WooCommerce Breadcrumbs</a></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h2>Best WordPress Breadcrumbs Plugin</h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"All-In-One-SEO\">1. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\">All In One SEO (AIOSEO)</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"561\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/All-In-One-SEO-AIOSEO-1024x561.png\" alt=\"All In One SEO - best breadcrumbs plugins\" class=\"wp-image-43907\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/All-In-One-SEO-AIOSEO-1024x561.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/All-In-One-SEO-AIOSEO-300x164.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/All-In-One-SEO-AIOSEO-768x421.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/All-In-One-SEO-AIOSEO-600x329.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/All-In-One-SEO-AIOSEO-109x60.png 109w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/All-In-One-SEO-AIOSEO-164x90.png 164w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/All-In-One-SEO-AIOSEO.png 1102w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\">AIOSEO</a> is the best WordPress SEO plugin that offers a <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/\">great number of features</a>, including a simple way of setting up breadcrumbs. This feature allows you to display breadcrumbs wherever you want and thus improves the user experience on your website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The setup is straightforward &#8211; you just need to navigate <strong>All in One SEO » General Settings</strong> in your WordPress admin dashboard.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To set up breadcrumbs, go to the <strong>Breadcrumbs</strong> tab, and toggle on <strong>Enable Breadcrumbs</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"730\" height=\"334\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Enable-Breadcrumbs.png\" alt=\"Enable Breadcrumbs\" class=\"wp-image-43908\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Enable-Breadcrumbs.png 730w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Enable-Breadcrumbs-300x137.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Enable-Breadcrumbs-60