t/uploads/2021/06/Flexy-Breadcrumb-768x249.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Flexy-Breadcrumb-600x194.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Flexy-Breadcrumb-185x60.png 185w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Flexy-Breadcrumb-278x90.png 278w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/flexy-breadcrumb/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Flexy Breadcrumb</a> is perhaps the easiest plugin to use on this list. It’s lightweight and integrates breadcrumbs directly in your desired locations. It has an active user community that uses the plugin to set up breadcrumbs on all pages and posts of their websites.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The plugin can be installed like any other plugin and after activation, you can use a shortcode to set up the breadcrumbs on the page.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Support For Schema:</strong> The plugin follows the website schema to streamline breadcrumb placement.&nbsp;</li><li><strong>Optimized Breadcrumb Design: </strong>The plugin allows you to change the separator, hierarchy, and color for the breadcrumb.</li><li><strong>Requires Shortcodes:</strong> The plugin requires some familiarity with editing pages and placing shortcodes.&nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>The plugin is free to use under the Open Source license.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"WooCommerce-Breadcrumbs\">7. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-breadcrumbs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">WooCommerce Breadcrumbs</a>&nbsp;</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-breadcrumbs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"937\" height=\"303\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/WooCommerce-Breadcrumbs-.png\" alt=\"WooCommerce Breadcrumbs\" class=\"wp-image-43914\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/WooCommerce-Breadcrumbs-.png 937w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/WooCommerce-Breadcrumbs--300x97.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/WooCommerce-Breadcrumbs--768x248.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/WooCommerce-Breadcrumbs--600x194.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/WooCommerce-Breadcrumbs--186x60.png 186w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/WooCommerce-Breadcrumbs--278x90.png 278w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This plugin is aimed at doing one single job: help restyle the default <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-breadcrumbs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">WooCommerce breadcrumbs</a>. With this plugin, you can easily disable the breadcrumb display on any page.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This plugin enhances the available options for WooCommerce breadcrumbs, and you can format them the way you like.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To use the plugin, simply install and activate it. Next, go to <strong>Settings » WC Breadcrumbs</strong> and set the options as you see fit.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features:</strong>&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>HTML Control: </strong>&nbsp;Use the plugin to edit the HTML template for better placement and styling of breadcrumbs.&nbsp;</li><li><strong>Complete Control Over Breadcrumbs: </strong>The plugin allows you to change the separator and related settings.&nbsp;</li><li><strong>Requires Web Development Exposure: </strong>This plugin mainly offers the tools to format the HTML code that displays the breadcrumbs on your site. This requires familiarity with web development and HTML code.&nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>&nbsp;The plugin is available for free.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Which Is the Best Breadcrumbs Plugin for WordPress?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>WordPress offers you a great choice of plugins in terms of usability and SEO. You can use any of the above Breadcrumb plugins to implement breadcrumbs on your site the way you want.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For best results, you should opt for <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\">AIOSEO</a> because it offers the best combination of features and options that improves usability and helps you beat the competition in terms of SEO. It gives you access to a set of advanced tools that takes your <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/ultimate-seo-guide/\">website SEO</a> to the next level.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this post helped you to find out the best WordPress breadcrumbs plugin.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You may also want to check out our <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/wordpress-seo/\">ultimate WordPress SEO guide</a> and&nbsp; <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-tutorials/seo-friendly-url-structure-for-wordpress/\">SEO Friendly URL Structure in WordPress</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What are you waiting for? Get started with the most powerful <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\">WordPress AIOSEO plugin</a> today.&nbsp;</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-breadcrumbs-plugins-for-wordpress/\">7 Best Breadcrumbs Plugins for WordPress (in 2021)</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"https://aioseo.com/best-breadcrumbs-plugins-for-wordpress/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a: